        <section>
          <section>
            <h2>So what about Web Games</h2>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h3>About Javascript Games</h3>
            <p>
              While Flash used to rule the roost of browser based games, HTML and Javascript games are now mature with many frameworks to support. 
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <p>
              One framework of special interest is <a href="https://phaser.io">Phaser</a> which as a low threshold for novice coders, good existing tutorials and a very active support forum.
            </p>
          </section>
          <section>
            <h3>Sample Platform Tutorial</h3>
